This paper focuses on natural language processing and machine learning techniques for information extraction, which are typically covered in the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves modeling and representation learning, which are relevant to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
